casebody.data:
John DOE, Sex Offender Registry Board No. 523878
v.
SEX OFFENDER REGISTRY BOARD. 18-P-120 Appeals Court of Massachusetts. Entered: June 20, 2019

The judgment affirming the board's classification of Doe as a level three sex offender is vacated, and the matter is remanded to the board for a new hearing consistent with the memorandum and order of the Appeals Court.
